&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But incase of verifyAllowed if the obj itself is null then we silently come out of the method thinking it is success.  But it should actually fail because in the verifyAllowed we expect the result.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13857609" author="apurtell" created="Fri, 27 Dec 2013 18:20:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the +1 Ram I will commit this a bit later. &lt;/p&gt;

